assets.description:
Explore FULL SEND METACARD.

Built on the Ethereum blockchain with a limited supply of 10,000 NFTs, the FULL SEND METACARD will give exclusive access to what FULL SEND does in the physical world and metaverse.

As a company, the FULL SEND goal is to launch more FULL SEND branded ventures, which include lounges, gyms, festivals, casinos, restaurants and more. FULL SEND is going international.

In addition, we will take these same ventures of products and physical locations and will launch them in the metaverse. This will include FULL SEND apparel, virtual stores, virtual festivals, metaverse casinos, and FULL SEND NFT recording artists. This list will continue to grow.

Owning a FULL SEND METACARD allows you to get in early on what is the beginning of a long journey for the FULL SEND brand.

collection.description:
Tony and Jay have been friends forever.  
Everyone says that they look like brothers from different mothers and the only significant difference in their appearance is that Tony has deep brown skin and Jay has a pale complexion - even more pale if he's been out the night before.
They love dressing up and going out.  They have eclectic tastes and - like many people - they go through phases, get bored and then try something new (or revisit something old).  
In terms of personality, most of the time Tony is quite laid back and chilled whereas Jay is often pretty wired and animated.

Each Tony and Jay image has been manually created to enable their personalities to shine through.  The images and the clothing items have primarily been created using Microsoft Powerpoint drawing tools, shapes and effects with some supplementary effects added using GIMP.
collection.name: Tony & Jay
